Class CorneredLoopEdge

  • java.lang.Object

      • com.fxgraph.edges.CorneredLoopEdge
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEdge, IGraphNode

    public class CorneredLoopEdge
extends AbstractEdge
    AbstractEdge implementation for representing an edge with two corners that connects a cell to itself.

    sirolf2009, ogallagher (javadoc)
